  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO REQUIRE THE MISSISSIPPI DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION TO PREPARE AND PUBLISH ON ITS WEBSITE INTERNET SAFETY RESOURCES; TO REQUIRE THE MISSISSIPPI DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION TO CREATE A CURRICULUM FOR SOCIAL MEDIA SAFETY; TO CREATE THE \"MISSISSIPPI KEEPING KIDS SAFE ONLINE ACT\"; TO REGULATE INTERACTIVE COMPUTER SERVICE PROVIDERS FROM OFFERING CERTAIN SERVICES TO MINORS; TO REGULATE CERTAIN PUBLIC PERFORMANCES IN COMMERCIAL ENTERPRISES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
